ommerce does have any product comparison feature by default. So, when you...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-free-woocommerce-products-compare-plugins/\">10+ Best Free WooCommerce Products Compare Plugins</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog\">Themebeez Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Editorial staff\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23281:\"\n<p>Neither WordPress nor WooCommerce does have any product comparison feature by default. So, when you wish to promote your sale allowing your customers to compare the products, you need to install WooCommerce products compare plugins. </p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The WooCommerce product compare plugins allows your customers to compare the products of your online store. It allows the customers to compare in between the products of a similar category or the pros and cons of similar products. With it, it can increase the product conversions and can give a branded look to your online store. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Best Free WooCommerce Products Compare Plugins:</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before you dive into the WooCommerce products compare plugins, check the <a href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-woocommerce-plugins-for-your-online-store/\" class=\"rank-math-link\">best WooCommerce plugins</a> that will help you to increase the sales of your online store. You may also be interested in <a href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-free-woocommerce-quick-view-plugins/\" class=\"rank-math-link\">WooCommerce Quick View</a> plugins and wishlist list plugins for WooCommerce as well. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The list given below is the list of WooCommerce products compare plugins that will help you to enhance the productivity of your online store and the user experience by comparing the products of your store. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">YITH WooCommerce Compare</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"629\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Compare-1-1024x629.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Compare Plugin ss\" class=\"wp-image-8780\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Compare-1-1024x629.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Compare-1-300x184.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Compare-1-768x472.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Compare-1-1536x944.png 1536w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Compare-1.png 1689w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"10+ Best Free WooCommerce Products Compare Plugins 55\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>YITH WooCommerce plugin is one of the most popular WooCommerce products compare plugin that allows the customers to compare products of your online store. With this plugin, you can view the difference between the products in which all products are saved in a complete table. You can set the product features in the product configuration with the WooCommerce attributes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This WooCommerce compare plugin is available for free and in the premium versions as well. FFor a single site you can get the plugin in £59. However, if you want to use the plugin for upto 6 sites of 30 sites, you can choose the package of £149 and £249 respecitively. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>WPML Compatible </li><li>Product SKY in the compare table</li><li>