ebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/wpastra.com-christmas-new-year-deal-300x145.jpg 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/wpastra.com-christmas-new-year-deal-768x372.jpg 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/wpastra.com-christmas-new-year-deal.jpg 1903w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"20+ Best SEO Optimized WordPress Themes 95\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best SEO Optimized WordPress themes is Astra. This SEO friendly theme is compatible with any kind of website. The theme is highly customizable and builds your website, considering the key factors of SEO. With this time, you will get in-depth AMP support, schema markups, and lightweight code. It can also work with page builders like; Divi, Thrive Architect, and Elementor. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The premium package of Astra starts from $50 with some basic features. However, the mini agency bundle of $169 and the agency bundle of $249 can give your website everything you want to make it better. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>One-to-one Support </li><li>Unlimited Website Usage </li><li>WP Portfolio Plugin </li><li>Extensive Training </li><li>Ultimate Address for Beaver Builder</li><li>Ultimate Address for Elementor </li><li>Woo Commerce </li><li>Supports all page builders</li><li>Lightweight </li><li>Pre-built website templates</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wpastra.com/\" target=\"_blank\">View Demo</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/astra/\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">OceanWP</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/oceanwp-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP Screen_Shot.Jpg\" class=\"wp-image-4105\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/oceanwp-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/oceanwp-300x225.jpg 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/oceanwp-768x576.jpg 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/oceanwp.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"20+ Best SEO Optimized WordPress Themes 96\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>OceanWP is a popular SEO optimized WordPress theme that is good for business and E-commerce sites. This lightweight theme is preferred by many, as it is very responsive. It has a beautiful and professional design along with customizable features. Also, it is mobile-friendly, and you can edit the setting from any device. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This WordPress theme is available in both free and premium versions. The premium version of the theme starts art $39. It is a super SEO WordPress theme preferred by many WordPress users. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Fast Page Load Time</li><li>eCommerce Ready </li><li>Fully Responsive </li><li>Professional design </li><li>Works with page builders</li><li>RTL &amp; Translation ready </li><li>In-built SEO base</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://oceanwp.org/\" target=\"_blank\">View Demo</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Neve</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Neve-Screen_Shot-1024x768.png\" alt=\"Neve Screen_Shot.Png\" class=\"wp-image-7066\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Neve-Screen_Shot-1024x768.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Neve-Screen_Shot-300x225.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Neve-Screen_Shot-768x576.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Neve-Screen_Shot.png 1142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"20+ Best SEO Optimized WordPress Themes 97\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are searching for the best SEO friendly theme for bloggers, here you have the best one. Neve is a popular SEO Optimized WordPress theme that is built for multipurpose. The theme is suitable for business, portfolio, travel agencies, as well as blogging. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The theme is available for personal use in $39, which includes some basic features. It offers business packages best for online shops in $59 and an agency features in $99, which is for the freelancers and agencies. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>SEO Optimized Code</li><li>WooCommerce ready </li><li>Responsive design </li><li>RTL &amp; Translation Ready </li><li>Supports page builders</li><li>Fast Page Load Time</li><li>Lightweight </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wp-themes.com/neve\" target=\"_blank\">View Demo</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/neve/\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Zakra</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zakra-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"Zakra Screen_Shot.Jpg\" class=\"wp-image-4108\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zakra-1024x768.jpg