2020/07/CosmosWp-1-1-768x488.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/CosmosWp-1-1.png 1288w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"20+ Best SEO Optimized WordPress Themes 99\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>CosmosWP is one of the best SEO Optimized WordPress themes that have a beautiful design and is easily customizable. This awesome theme has a unique style and is suitable for blogs, business, entertainment, education, photography, along with travel websites. Users can download this theme easily and can also customize using basic page builders. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This SEO Optimized WordPress theme is absolutely free. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>E-commerce ready </li><li>Header and footer builder</li><li>High Speed and Performance</li><li>Advanced Typography and colors</li><li>Easy Digital Download</li><li>Works with page builders</li><li>Fully Responsive</li><li>WordPress Plugins Comtabile</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.cosmoswp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">View Demo</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/cosmoswp/\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sinatra</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"849\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sinatra-1-849x1024.png\" alt=\"Sinatra SEO Optimized WordPress theme\" class=\"wp-image-8431\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sinatra-1-849x1024.png 849w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sinatra-1-249x300.png 249w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sinatra-1-768x926.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Sinatra-1-12