reativo-Theme-featured-image-2048x1063.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"20+ Best SEO Optimized WordPress Themes 101\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Creativo theme is a fully SEO optimized &amp; mobile-friendly theme that comes heavily packed with a lot of other features. Preferred by both big and small blog owners and companies, it offers a lot of customization across all channels, demos included. Along with over 180 Creativo Blocks packed, WooCommerce-ready makes it easily one of the top themes for anyone looking to build a website with quality and readiness in the main focus.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>SEO optimized</li><li>WooCommerce ready</li><li>WPBakery builder</li><li>Responsive</li><li>WPML ready</li><li>Pre-built demos</li><li>Slideshow builder tools</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://rockythemes.com/creativo/\" target=\"_blank\">View Demo</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Schema Lite</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"701\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/schema-lite-1024x701.png\" alt=\"schema lite screenshot \" class=\"wp-image-8434\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/schema-lite-1024x701.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/schema-lite-300x205.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/schema-lite-768x526.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/schema-lite.png 1337w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"20+ Best SEO Optimized WordPress Themes 102\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Schema Lite is a popular SEO Optimized WordPress theme that is ideal for creating blogs. This free theme is popular among travel, entertainment, fashion, a