n\n\n\n<p>As Wordfence is the most powerful among the WordPress security plugins, it protects malicious traffic, hacking, and malware. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Blocks malicious traffic</li><li>Scans malware to check themes, plugins, and files before uploading </li><li>Monitors analytics</li><li>Two-factor Authentication (2FA) </li><li>Limited failed login attempts</li><li>Runs on your own server </li><li>Single Dashboard</li><li>Removes hacked file</li><li>WordPress Security Scanning </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordfence/\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads Wordfence Security</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">All in one WP Security &amp; Firewall</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/All-in-one-WP-Security-Firewall-Screen_Shot-1024x478.png\" alt=\"All in one WP Security &amp; Firewall Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7870\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/All-in-one-WP-Security-Firewall-Screen_Shot-1024x478.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/All-in-one-WP-Security-Firewall-Screen_Shot-300x140.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/All-in-one-WP-Security-Firewall-Screen_Shot-768x359.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/All-in-one-WP-Security-Firewall-Screen_Shot.png 1257w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" title=\"13+ Best WordPress Security Plugins 116\"><figcaption>imag</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p